<span id="freeTextContainer103507808401417354">The last half of this book really redeemed a slow first half. I generally like slow books, but the first half felt a bit bland and dull. However, the final half was exactly what I loved about Bradshaw’s writing, gripping, magical, believable, thematic with characters that come to life. I would recommend this second installation of the series and just encourage others to push through, it’s worth it. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


