<span id="freeTextContainer16329052362368432957">In my opinion, if you are going to write about Arthurian legend, you should maintain the classic tragedy and conflict. I guess I would have appreciated this book more if she hadn&apos;t turned it into yet another Arthur story. Her characters are not compatible with any other Arthur book I have read, and she has lost the juiciest parts of the legend. I don&apos;t plan on read the third book of the trilogy. </span>
