              <span id="reviewTextContainer29279447" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15994412786864789755">One of the more realist works on the Matter of Britain but the realism tends to suck the magic out of the thing. It was good enough that I felt compelled to read the whole trilogy but I had greater expectations about the writing.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

